{"tid":1536990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【召換大埔人】9月5號朝0930，大埔區議會旁聽席要人","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T01:15:04.000Z","uid":266028,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"23dc06b0088c19791656f5e2674ec804f6359153","tid":1536990,"uid":266028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:42:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tp/doc/2016_2019/tc/dc_meetings_agenda/TPDC_A5_20190905.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Ftp%2Fdoc%2F2016_2019%2Ftc%2Fdc_meetings_agenda%2FTPDC_A5_20190905.pdf&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vtMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=d4653e8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tp/doc/2016_2019/tc/dc_meetings_agenda/TPDC_A5_20190905.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n【召換大埔人】9月5號朝0930，大埔區議會旁聽席要人<br />\n【召換大埔人】9月5號朝0930，大埔區議會旁聽席要人<br />\n【召換大埔人】9月5號朝0930，大埔區議會旁聽席要人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/titqmxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtitqmxX.jpg&h=de5a69f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qN0DGxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqN0DGxX.jpg&h=a6d3b2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8CFUSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8CFUSY.jpg&h=11e8a0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">P牌仔開post<br />\n有錯請細力屌</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>議程2對大埔區議會主席黃碧嬌議員作出不信任動議<br />\n議程11要求警方交代批評太和邨居民阻撓警方辦案 議程12 805 810當日大埔區集會遊行</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 點解旁聽咁重要？</span></strong><br />\n睇番上次七月大埔區議會大會，班廢老藍C一早坐定定係旁聽席，同個仆街主席裡應外合，鐘意講乜就講乜，成個現場輿論俾佢地帶住走，傳媒影旁聽仲多過影議員發言<br />\n<br />\n21個議席，只有6個係民主派，孤軍作戰<br />\n本身佢地已經要係會上，以6敵15<br />\n休會仲要俾班藍C無差別你一句我一句咁攻擊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 要幾多人？做乜？</span></span><br />\n基本上我評估對家都會吹大雞，所以要早過佢地，唯一希望係9月4號晚通宵留守。<strong>位置係大埔綜合大樓4樓升降機大堂，</strong>有冷氣，室內，對面街有2間通宵茶記，華X華X<br />\n<br />\n估計果朝萬人空巷，要登記先入到，拎到旁聽席Label當你贏，只有30個位<br />\n<br />\n黎唔係要支持果6個議員，個目標係令到藍絲廢老無得鳩叫，霸曬佢地D位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3. 有無用？</strong></span><br />\n核彈都唔割，兄弟爬山各自努力，民選議員都有民選議員該做的事<br />\n<br />\n唔想早兩日深水埗北區區議會大會發生既事再重現<br />\n今次係今屆會期最後一次大會，無下一次<br />\n下一次可能已經面目全非<br />\n街頭有街頭抗爭<br />\n議會亦一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4. 和定勇？</span><br />\n其實做咁多，都係姿態，唔想次次都俾班共狗人多玩曬。我知好辛苦，無啦啦要係出面訓一晚，為既只係霸住個旁聽位，但任何方法都要試，反正可能係最後一次&hellip;&hellip;尋日我係警署門口，著住校服，見到佢地民主聯盟開記招，佢地都用緊佢地方法去表達訴求同選擇企係抗爭者一方<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><em>早過班藍絲早過班藍絲早過班藍絲</em></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3e78c5d7597597ad1eab45fb8b1ed5e3abd3059d","tid":1536990,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:43:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e911d08e9a30cdba5d586d2bbd8beaf1cabdd5f","tid":1536990,"uid":266028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:43:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09a34511a0d58d4e12bb5e68ce2848ab789d9286","tid":1536990,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"f0ac6dbec300ee5f087b6c999db834a764b189ce","tid":1536990,"uid":266028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:45:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96d60e6d6bb58cba32e3190b27f9a58159f495dd","tid":1536990,"uid":112093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推到比大埔谷知"},{"pid":"59ab567f7a786f1daefe022593dd9667e67ee8cf","tid":1536990,"uid":116958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"值得一試"},{"pid":"3235bde0b6149bea18f945eb5e97cbe39f40cdc4","tid":1536990,"uid":266028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:56:58.000Z","msg"